reviews.text:
Been getting my party supplies here.
It was easy liaising via WhatsApp with the kind owner who always help to ensure that my event will look great and amazing no matter if its a family birthday or company event.

Always coming back here !
Went to get balloons for my girl birthday and served by Yoko, she is a patient and nice young lady. She also recommended the design for me to choose . Price is reasonable.

This pop up store is like a gem in this place. Really great for parties, events and gathering. They have almost anything but it is good for you to come in advance in case you need to order anything, or else, you can just grab whatever options they have there which is fairly quite a lot of options too!
Seller is friendly, nice & responsive. Whatever request she will do her best to fulfill your requirements. Will go back to her again. Highly recommended üëç

Very good service with good advice and suggestions on colour matching with your party themes. Friendly staff who are patient in helping to make the perfect choice for the party! Would come again in future for party ideas!
